data.description: Welcome home! Move in ready. New Friarsgate. Perfect starter home! Very open floor plan. All appliances will stay - including microwave, fridge, and w/d. New stainless dishwasher. New kitchen counter tops, sink, and faucet! Gorgeous bay window in breakfast area. Wet bar in living room. New carpet. Tile floors. Cozy wood burning fireplace. Crown molding. 4 LARGE bedrooms! 3 full baths. French doors open from dining room onto full-length deck with built in benches! Fully fenced backyard. HVAC system is only 4 years old! Roof was replaced 6 years ago. FREE 12 month home warranty! Lex/Rich District 5 Schools.
